Interface Player

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Carrier, CommandSender, Entity, Equipable, Identifiable, LivingEntity, Locatable, Permissible, PluginMessageRecipient

    public interface Player
extends LivingEntity, CommandSender, PluginMessageRecipient, Equipable
    A Player represents the in-game entity of a human playing on a server.
